  </div>
</div>

<h2 id="tm-pico">tm-pico</h2>

<p style="margin-bottom:2em">A cute sans-serif with a crude geometric feel and minimal optical corrections. Pico supports Latin Plus (incl. Pinyin &amp; Vietnamese) and basic Cyrillic â€” for now.</p>

